<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ط م ا:</span> <span class="c2">(طَمَا)</span> الْمَاءُ مِنْ بَابِ سَمَا وَ <span class="c2">(طَمَى)</span> يَطْمِي بِالْكَسْرِ <span class="c2">(طُمِيًّا)</span> بِوَزْنِ مُضِيٍّ أَيْضًا فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(طَامٍ)</span> إِذَا ارْتَفَعَ وَمَلَأَ النَّهْرَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>